tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"睇左咁多答案<br />\n如果係正向關係<br />\n<br />\n幾個答案都係0.35/0.25 = 0.7142<br />\n<br />\n姐係 A升1% B就會升0.7142%<br />\n好啦～ 可以放番落個excel到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝大大～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係都A/B=135/125=101/B<br />\nB=93.5185<br />\nB跌6.4815%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"錯呀聰明"},{"pid":"501bc08e5e067d4345e49b4f487f17a1cd300078","tid":2242892,"uid":255542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"以為係1q題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲諗著睇李斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65585d706761e0dcc5b5f939da47b2c6acf3ac36","tid":2242892,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"比率黎炸wo"},{"pid":"676810b4acb35d80ee7813b63c4f93acda24cefc","tid":2242892,"uid":324704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"樓主鳩作題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e68fe5c9812c4a49738395d9f0adff755cb7bbd","tid":2242892,"uid":163881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c73f0b42da86c6c29e3a0b6b4cf3b524cc50f257","tid":2242892,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ed5fd4a1d51e97d586235254ff7941dcc116ac3","tid":2242892,"uid":38904,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"跌13%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫幫手<br />\n唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"咪教咗你囉，有引伸波幅又有時間值<br />\n中邊都輸撚死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"40ac7fd5c8a5b2a39734b70c27d9bcb8ff22199c","tid":2242892,"uid":93712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"唔同人假設唔同 model 會有唔同答案，所以上面先咁多人話唔夠資料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">1. 上面 0.7143%</span></strong> （例如樓主置頂 #67）類似 simple interest：假設 A 同 B 符合<br />\nA(t) = A₀ (1+at);  B(t) = B₀ (1+bt)<br />\n然後喺某個時間 A 升咗 35% 而 B 升咗 25%<br />\n1+at₂ = 1.35;  1+bt₂ = 1.25<br />\nat₂ = 0.35;  bt₂ = 0.25<br />\na/b = 7/5<br />\n問當 A 升咗 1% 時， B 升咗幾多？<br />\n1+at₁ = 1.01<br />\nat₁ = 0.01<br />\nbt₁ = 0.01 / (a/b) = 0.05/7 = 0.7143...%<br />\n----<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>2. 另外上面 0.7426%</strong></span> （例如 #81 、 #29）類似 compound interest ：假設 A 同 B 符合<br />\nA(t) = A₀ (1+a)^t;  B(t) = B₀ (1+b)^t<br />\n然後喺某個時間 A 升咗 35% 而 B 升咗 25%<br />\n(1+a)^t₂ = 1.35;  (1+b)^t₂ = 1.25<br />\nt₂ log (1+a) = log 1.35;  t₂ log(1+b) = log 1.25<br />\n[log(1+a)] / [log(1+b)] = (log 1.35) / (log 1.25)<br />\n問當 A 升咗 1% 時， B 升咗幾多？<br />\n(1+a)^t₁ = 1.01<br />\nt₁ log(1+a) = log 1.01<br />\nt₁ log(1+b) = log 1.01 / (log 1.35 / log 1.25) = log 1.01 * log 1.25 / log 1.35<br />\n(1+b)^t₁ = exp(log 1.01 * log 1.25 / log 1.35)<br />\n = 1.01 ^ (log 1.25 / log 1.35)<br />\n = 1.007426...<br />\n = 1 + 0.7426...%<br />\n----<br />\n我個人同意 <strong><span class=\"red\">2.</span></strong> 個 model 同答案 <strong><span class=\"red\">0.7426%</span></strong> ，因為無論喺任何時間開始計都好，只要 A 升 35% ， B 就會升 25% ，比較符合問題"}}